{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_10_02",
  "title": "赤崎こころ 2話 悪魔……いや、kanaさん",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "よし、これで今日の仕事は終わりだな\n今からなら、午前中には学校に着きそうだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ that concludes today's work.\nIf you leave now‚ you should be able to get to school before noon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "わー、やったー、学校だー\n嬉しいなー、早く行きたいなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ yay‚ school!\nI'm so happyー‚ I want to go quicklyー",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.8334695816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ようやくテスト期間も終わったっていうのに\n全く行きたそうじゃないな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though the exam period has finally ended‚\nyou don't look like you want to go at all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.8948751608
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "テストも終わったし、お仕事に集中したいんですよー\nせっかくkanaさんとのユニットもいい感じですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The exams are over‚ so I want to focus on work.\nSince the unit with Kana-san is going well‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.1871886571,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、行かなかったら行かなかったで\n大量に宿題を出されるから嫌なんですけどねー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ if I didn't go‚ it wouldn't be good either.\nI'd hate getting assigned tons of homework‚ you see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2205219905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.0293865361
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そう言うなよ。テストの結果、赤点もなくて良かった\nじゃないか。俺も勉強に付き合った甲斐があるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't talk like that. It's good that you didn't fail the exam.\nIt means my time spent helping you study was worth it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それに、こころの言う通り\nkanaさんとのユニットも本当に順調みたいだしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ just as Kokoro said‚\nthe unit with Kana-san seems to be going really well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.7171640235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前じゃないですか～。こころとkanaさん……\nいえ、kanaちゃんは大の仲良しなんですから～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn't that obvious~? Kokoro and Kana-san…\nNo‚ Kana-chan is the best of friends with me~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5187306088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.9641019979
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "この間のお昼の番組でも\n約束した通り、息ピッタリのトークを披露出来ましたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On the daytime show the other day‚\nwe delivered perfectly synchronized talk‚ just as we promised.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9853965125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "一緒にやってる生配信、『どこかな？　ココかな？\n放送部』も同接数凄いことになってるんですよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The live stream we're doing together‚ \"Where is it? Is it here?\nBroadcasting Club‚\" also has an incredible number of concurrent viewers.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.5187298459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.7558255671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや……配信中とかだけ、仲良しアピールしてるって\n俺、普通に知ってるからな？　全部見てたからな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… I know you're only making it look like you're close during the stream or something.\nI know it perfectly well‚ okay? I've been watching everything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "嫌ですねぇ。会議を覗き見しておいて開き直るだなんて\n怜ちゃんも言ってた通り、覗き魔ですよ。おー、こわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How unpleasant. Peeking into our meeting and then acting brazenly—\nJust like Rei said‚ you're a peeping tom. Oh‚ scary.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.1486392023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.5318798858
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "ま、そんな覗き魔な{user}さんでも\nBIG4の広い心で許してあげますね～。きゃはっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ even a peeping tom like {user}-san‚\nI'll forgive you with the generous heart of a BIG4. Kyahaha",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.5486392023,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "なんか妙なところで\nkanaさんの影響を受けてる気がするんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel like you're being influenced by Kana-san\nin some strange way…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.9488359609
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.9488359609
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ学校に着いちゃうので、こころは失礼します\n年上の彼氏がいる、なんて噂が立ったら困りますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll be arriving at school soon‚ so I'll be taking my leave.\nIt would be trouble if rumors spread that I have an older boyfriend.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.8681804342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "その前に一つだけ……。悪かった。こころが学校で\nうまくいってないこと、今まで気付くことが出来なくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just one thing before that… I'm sorry. I wasn't able to notice\nthat things weren't going well for you at school until now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.5880903085
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "え……。あ～……どっかから知っちゃったんですね\n別にそんな、申し訳なさそうにしなくていいですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh… Ah… you found out from somewhere‚ didn't you?\nYou don't have to look so sorry about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.8899978959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.0057094734
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんには、随分前に\n冗談ぽく話しただけですから知らなくて当然ですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I only mentioned it to {user}-san\nas a joke‚ so it's natural that you didn't know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.3273706822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "大体、こころだってもう慣れっこで\n今更そんな重く受け止めてませんでしたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ Kokoro is already used to it now.\nI wasn't taking it that seriously anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5566645626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.1938558103
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "そんなので気付くなんて、無理もいいとこです\n……でも、どうして学校のことを？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's completely impossible to have noticed it like that.\n…But‚ why did you ask about school?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.0233373329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんがチクった……訳じゃないですね\nあの人、そういう話は他人に言わないですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kana-san didn't tell on me… right?\nThat person doesn't tell those kinds of stories to others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.2900029823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.7337733111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "悪いけど……担任の先生に問い合わせて\n学校でのこころの様子を聞かせてもらったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ but… I contacted your homeroom teacher\nand asked about how things were going for you at school.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.8333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "この前話した時、学校が好きじゃなさそうだったから\n……勝手なことをしてすまない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You didn't seem to like school when we talked before.\n…I'm sorry for doing something presumptuous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.999995931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174.379102119
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_02-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～……仕方ないから許してあげます\nkanaさんにも言いましたが、他の人には秘密ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa~… I'll forgive you since it can't be helped.\nI told Kana-san‚ but keep it a secret from others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.2457539564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 182.3576053781
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
